{"id": 253, "genre": 1000, "title": "论自拍是怎么把好诗给毁了的", "description": "“从前的日色变得慢/车，马，邮件都慢/一生只够爱一个人”……木心的《从前慢》已经超越“愿得一人心，白首不相离”成为新自拍必配诗句。\r\n", "record_count": 2071, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194248dEp1btq3njG7ws0J.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-02-05T22:17:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 189, "title": "论自拍是怎么把好诗给毁了的", "content": "论自拍是怎么把好诗给毁了的\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1596, "content": "从前的日色变得慢/车，马，邮件都慢", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192737Snfv13LPGUYDIdOu.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1598, "content": "我已累极/全忘了疲惫/我悭吝自守/一路布施着回来", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192737TkaV0AQvRjHPghdN.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1599, "content": "树啊/水啊/都很悲伤的", "image": "img/option/option/201606071927376ezbnRW28FG5JgBX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1600, "content": "其实，睡你和被你睡是差不多的", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192737qQ5ozuNwLOFeTmY1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1602, "content": "把你的影子/加点盐/腌起来/风干", "image": "img/option/option/201606071927380lHtEDc5o3eIa1hn.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1603, "content": "如何让你遇见我/在我最美丽的时刻", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192738GePLSqipwYmjVyrE.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1604, "content": "这是一个港口。我在这里爱你。我在这里爱你,而且地平线徒然的隐藏你。", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192738rTgdulcXqvizQHJG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1606, "content": "在夜色中/我有三次受难：流浪、爱情、生存", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192738o8RiF7zclvrBX4y0.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}